text: "We Close Our Eyes" is a 1985 debut single by English pop duo Go West. It went to number 4 in New Zealand, number 5 in the United Kingdom, number 8 in Australia, number 9 in Italy, number 11 in Ireland, number 14 in Belgium and Germany, number 19 in Switzerland, number 22 in the Netherlands and number 41 in the United States. == References == Category:1985 songs Category:Debut singles Category:Go West songs
title: We Close Our Eyes
